<div class="story-body">
  <p>ITU has been measuring GCI every other year since 2014, and the 2018 index is the third in the series. 
    The valuable part of the index is that the countries are compared to themselves, so how they handle the five dimensions doesn't get overshadowed by the fact that it is a smaller country, or a country with lower GDP compared to its neighbors. </p>
</div>

